{"book": 66, "chapter": 18, "sections": [{"type": "heading", "heading": "巴比倫傾倒"}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "此後，我看見另有一位有大權柄的天使從天降下，地就因他的榮耀發光。 "}, {"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他大聲喊着說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 巴比倫大城傾倒了！傾倒了！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "成了鬼魔的住處"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "和各樣污穢之靈的巢穴，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "並各樣污穢可憎之雀鳥的巢穴。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "因為列國都被她邪淫大怒的酒傾倒了。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "地上的君王與她行淫；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "地上的客商因她奢華太過就發了財。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我又聽見從天上有聲音說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我的民哪，你們要從那城出來，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "免得與她一同有罪，受她所受的災殃；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "因她的罪惡滔天；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "她的不義，神已經想起來了。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "她怎樣待人，也要怎樣待她，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "按她所行的加倍地報應她；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "用她調酒的杯加倍地調給她喝。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "她怎樣榮耀自己，怎樣奢華，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "也當叫她照樣痛苦悲哀，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因她心裏說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我坐了皇后的位，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "並不是寡婦，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "決不至於悲哀。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "所以在一天之內，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "她的災殃要一齊來到，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "就是死亡、悲哀、饑荒。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "她又要被火燒盡了，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為審判她的主神大有能力。"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "地上的君王，素來與她行淫、一同奢華的，看見燒她的煙，就必為她哭泣哀號。 "}, {"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "因怕她的痛苦，就遠遠地站着說：哀哉！哀哉！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 巴比倫大城，堅固的城啊，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "一時之間你的刑罰就來到了。"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "地上的客商也都為她哭泣悲哀，因為沒有人再買他們的貨物了； "}, {"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "這貨物就是金、銀、寶石、珍珠、細麻布、紫色料、綢子、朱紅色料、各樣香木、各樣象牙的器皿、各樣極寶貴的木頭，和銅、鐵、漢白玉的器皿， "}, {"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "並肉桂、荳蔻、香料、香膏、乳香、酒、油、細麵、麥子、牛、羊、車、馬，和奴僕、人口。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 巴比倫哪，你所貪愛的果子離開了你；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你一切的珍饈美味"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "和華美的物件也從你中間毀滅，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "決不能再見了。"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "販賣這些貨物、藉着她發了財的客商，因怕她的痛苦，就遠遠地站着哭泣悲哀，說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "哀哉！哀哉！這大城啊，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "素常穿着細麻、"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "紫色、朱紅色的衣服，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "又用金子、寶石，和珍珠為妝飾。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "一時之間，這麼大的富厚就歸於無有了。"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "凡船主和坐船往各處去的，並眾水手，連所有靠海為業的，都遠遠地站着， "}, {"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "看見燒她的煙，就喊着說：「有何城能比這大城呢？」 "}, {"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他們又把塵土撒在頭上，哭泣悲哀，喊着說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "哀哉！哀哉！這大城啊。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "凡有船在海中的，都因她的珍寶成了富足！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "她在一時之間就成了荒場！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "天哪，眾聖徒、眾使徒、眾先知啊，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你們都要因她歡喜，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為神已經在她身上伸了你們的冤。"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "有一位大力的天使舉起一塊石頭，好像大磨石，扔在海裏，說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 巴比倫大城也必這樣猛力地被扔下去，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "決不能再見了。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "彈琴、作樂、吹笛、吹號的聲音，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "在你中間決不能再聽見；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "各行手藝人在你中間決不能再遇見；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "推磨的聲音在你中間決不能再聽見；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "燈光在你中間決不能再照耀；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "新郎和新婦的聲音，在你中間決不能再聽見。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你的客商原來是地上的尊貴人；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "萬國也被你的邪術迷惑了。"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "先知和聖徒，並地上一切被殺之人的血，都在這城裏看見了。"}]}]}